  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 5
  Paragraph: 17
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
\"You weren't careful enough!" said Confucius. "Since you've already
broken the law and gotten yourself into trouble like this, what do you
expect to gain by coming to me now?"
